    desc:"East from Girona through Banyoles lake and down to the Costa Brava fishing village of Sa Tuna. Empty roads in spring and autumn, limestone cliffs, turquoise water. The return climbs back through La Bisbal — stop for a coffee and a look around the ceramics town.",

